{"tid":2078200,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚同老母攤牌 但變左佢嬲我","createTime":"2020-06-25T00:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T11:56:57.000Z","uid":326724,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"806fa0f309facb72335d1f29f11be5d99039e1a1","tid":2078200,"uid":326724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T00:34:36.000Z","msg":"話說我琴日喊左成日都停唔到<br />\n好想大叫冇得叫<br />\n我真係第一次崩潰到係條街到喊<br />\n所以我決定左同老母講我忍左好耐<br />\n但我唔明<br />\n點解會變左佢嬲9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重話我唔記得我有講佢壞話<br />\n唔get wo點撚算好<br />\n係米因為我喊嘅時候都唔撚出聲佢理解唔到我有幾傷心<br />\n大檸樂我係米可以去死先<br />\n次次唔開心想同佢講都比佢鬧返轉頭<br />\n我係米猿左啦"},{"pid":"57f697eff1a42e96dcd31d9cd95eaf4a4b5a4f7e","tid":2078200,"uid":326724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T00:36:00.000Z","msg":"我係米要係佢面前表演一次冇出聲但不停大叫嘅喊聲"},{"pid":"c1d6df57f70faf73fdb406a845f7b9afa6969c8f","tid":2078200,"uid":218407,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T00:36:50.000Z","msg":"米你老母"},{"pid":"4e884be0b92ba52cafc6aee7d0c2a6195d0493e8","tid":2078200,"uid":326724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T00:37:09.000Z","msg":"哇 原來我先係衰人黎 原來我一直都誤解左 我嘅存在先係家庭嘅污點"},{"pid":"6f9b3986d25db7755273b100492e8b2869d19436","tid":2078200,"uid":326724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1d6df57f70faf73fdb406a845f7b9afa6969c8f","tid":2078200,"uid":218407,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T00:36:50.000Z","msg":"米你老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T00:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44057cff03ec6443fc7da16279db64bddee37926","tid":2078200,"uid":326724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T00:38:30.000Z","msg":"真係好崩潰"},{"pid":"78e49ceebc8ecb5a928d4ae884cee94ebd0cd1cc","tid":2078200,"u